{"id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0020", "text": "大概我已 用光了運氣", "structure": {"line_index": 20, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 5, 5, 2, 3, 5, 2, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daai6", "koi3", "ngo5", "ji5", "jung6", "gwong1", "liu5", "wan6", "hei3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "大概", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "已", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "用光", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "運氣", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "XBF", "artists": ["薛凱琪"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1081", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0019", "next_line_id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0021", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0021", "text": "熱吻過 教我怎捨得憎你", "structure": {"line_index": 21, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 4, 4, 5, 9, 9, 3, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jit6", "man5", "gwo3", "gaau3", "ngo5", "zam2", "se2", "dak1", "zang1", "nei5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "熱吻", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "教", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怎", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "捨得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "憎", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "XBF", "artists": ["薛凱琪"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1081", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0020", "next_line_id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0022", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0022", "text": "舊愛之中 明顯叫我 最幸福那是你", "structure": {"line_index": 22, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 3, 3, 0, 9, 4, 5, 4, 2, 3, 5, 2, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["gau6", "oi3", "zi1", "zung1", "ming4", "hin2", "giu3", "ngo5", "zeoi3", "hang6", "fuk1", "naa5", "si6", "nei5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "舊愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "之中", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "明顯", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "叫", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "幸福", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "XBF", "artists": ["薛凱琪"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1081", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0021", "next_line_id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0023", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0023", "text": "只怪我太不爭氣", "structure": {"line_index": 23, "char_count": 7}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 4, 5, 4, 3, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zi2", "gwaai3", "ngo5", "taai3", "bat1", "zang1", "hei3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "只", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怪我太", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不爭氣", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "XBF", "artists": ["薛凱琪"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1081", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0022", "next_line_id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0024", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0024", "text": "其實 犯遍了錯誤先碰着你", "structure": {"line_index": 24, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 2, 4, 5, 4, 2, 3, 4, 2, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["kei4", "sat6", "faan6", "pin3", "liu5", "co3", "ng6", "sin1", "pung3", "zoek6", "nei5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "其實", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "犯遍", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "錯誤", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "先", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "碰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "着", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "XBF", "artists": ["薛凱琪"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1081", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0023", "next_line_id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0025", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
{"id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0025", "text": "自信我會懂 怎去愛你", "structure": {"line_index": 25, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 5, 9, 9, 4, 4, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zi6", "seon3", "ngo5", "dung2", "zam2", "heoi3", "oi3", "nei5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "自信", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "懂", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怎去", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "XBF", "artists": ["薛凱琪"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1081", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0024", "next_line_id": "lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MTA4MQ_0026", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
